<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Deleted</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .confirmation-container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 500px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      color: #28a745;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .btn {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="confirmation-container">
    <h1>Account Deleted Successfully</h1>
    <p>Your account has been successfully deleted. We're sorry to see you go.</p>
    <p>If this was a mistake, please contact support immediately.</p>
    <a href="/" class="btn">Go to Registration</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
